Title: Among Us
Description:
We could use those recruits to bolster us, but those dreadful undead are harrying our supply lines! They will all be put in the ground permanently, soon enough.

Could you check on our stockpiles to make sure we've got enough for your recruits? Of course the good stuff has already gone up to Fenris Keep for the Commander, but everyone has to eat.

Well, almost everyone.

Get a move on, lieutenant.
ObjectivesText: Plant Explosive Plague and eliminate Scarlet Archmages without being discovered.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Dark Ranger Velonara on the north side of Fenris Isle.
